1. Izađi na *teren* i pripremi igralište za utakmicu. (Go out to the *field* and prepare the pitch for the match.)
2. Njegov omiljeni *teren* je teniski teren. (His favorite *terrain* is the tennis court.)
3. Naša ekipa je pobijedila na *terenu* protivničke momčadi. (Our team won on the *field* of the opposing team.)
4. Novinar je dobio nalog da istraži *teren* o navodnom korupcijskom skandalu. (The journalist received an order to investigate the *ground* of the alleged corruption scandal.)
5. *Terenski* radnik je zadužen za održavanje puteva u planinskim predjelima. (The *field* worker is responsible for maintaining roads in mountainous areas.)
6. Planiramo izgraditi novi *teren* za odbojku u školskom dvorištu. (We plan to build a new *court* for volleyball in the school yard.)
7. Naš tim se priprema za važan susret na *terenu* protiv našeg najvećeg rivala. (Our team is preparing for an important match on the *field* against our biggest rival.)
8. Poljoprivrednik mora pažljivo birati *teren* za uzgoj određenih kultura. (The farmer must carefully choose the *ground* for cultivating certain crops.)
9. Kada sam stigao na *teren*, shvatio sam da sam zaboravio svoju loptu kod kuće. (When I arrived on the *field*, I realized that I had forgotten my ball at home.)
10. *Terenska* vozila su neophodna za posao geologa koji istražuju rudna bogatstva. (The *field* vehicles are necessary for the work of geologists who explore mineral resources.)